title: Thoughts of the Election Results ( Jeezy Inteview)
itunes:title: Thoughts of the Election Results ( Jeezy Inteview)
description:
Today on the show you know we had to discuss the heavily waiting results of the election, and it looks like we got a new president, but we know not all might be happy about this so we opened up the phone lines to hear what our listeners thought about the election. Moreover, we also had Jeezy come in where he spoke about his new podcast, verzuz battle and more. Also, Charlamagne gave "Donkey of the Day" to Van Jones for getting Beyonce and Mary J Blige songs confused.
